headline: A New Generation of Renovators Is On the Rise: New CRAFTSMAN® Survey Finds, Despite Uncertainty, Younger DIYers Feel Confident, Motivated to Accomplish Home Improvement Projects This Year
summary: Despite a backdrop of uncertainty, younger homeowners don't plan to hit pause on their planned home improvement projects. Rather than waiting or compromising, many Millennials and Gen Zers are rolling up their sleeves and literally taking matters into their own hands, according to newly released research from CRAFTSMAN®, the most trusted and recommended brand in Tools & Outdoor* for today's DIYers.
